                  identity by obscuring your IP address.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div
              class="feature-card is-bordered has-text-centered is-feature-reveal"
            >
              <div class="card-title">
                <h4>Unrestricted access.</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="card-icon">
                <img src="/img/icons/rocket.svg" />
              </div>
              <div class="card-text">
                <p>
                  effortlessly enables you to access all types of content and
                  sidestep local online restrictions by altering your virtual
                  location.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-4">
            <div
              class="feature-card is-bordered has-text-centered is-feature-reveal"
            >
              <div class="card-title">
